This paper deals with frequent itemset mining, which is a common task in data mining and falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses deduction rules and the reduction of the result of a mining operation, which are topics related to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also presents experimental results, which could fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) or information theory (cs.IT).
